snippet.title: Intellivision - Beauty & the Beast © 1982 Imagic - Gameplay
snippet.description:
DESCRIPTION
That big bully's got the girl. It's you to the rescue. Climb the building, floor by floor. But watch out! Our fearsome foe is angrily tossing boulders. The higher you go, the harder the going gets. Best time to the top wins the game.
